Child Sexual Abuse and Exploitation (CSAE) Safety Standards

Effective Date: 2026-02-22
App Name: SparkLove

1. Zero Tolerance Policy

SparkLove has a zero-tolerance policy toward any form of child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE).

We strictly prohibit the creation, distribution, possession, or promotion of any content that involves sexual abuse, exploitation, or endangerment of minors.

Any violation of this policy will result in immediate action, including account suspension or permanent removal, and may be reported to appropriate authorities.

2. Prohibited Content

The following is strictly prohibited on our platform:

Any sexual content involving minors.

Content that exploits, abuses, or endangers children.

Grooming behavior or attempts to establish inappropriate relationships with minors.

Sharing or requesting sexually explicit images involving minors.

Any activity that promotes or facilitates child exploitation.

Users found engaging in such activities will be permanently banned.

3. Reporting Mechanism

We provide mechanisms for users to report inappropriate or illegal content.

If you encounter content or behavior that violates these standards, please report it immediately through:

ðŸ“§ Email: federicolcrovetto@gmail.com

All reports are reviewed promptly and handled with strict confidentiality.

4. Cooperation with Law Enforcement

We fully cooperate with law enforcement agencies and relevant authorities in the investigation of child sexual abuse or exploitation.

When legally required, we will provide necessary information to assist investigations.

5. Age Restrictions

SparkLove is intended for users aged 15 and older.
We do not knowingly allow minors to create accounts or use the platform.

If we become aware that a minor has registered, we will take immediate steps to remove the account.

6. Content Moderation

We actively monitor and review reported content and reserve the right to remove any content or accounts that violate our policies.

We are committed to maintaining a safe and respectful environment for all users.

